                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Mais l’horreur d’être ne ploiera point nos genoux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Dans nos yeux, le regard des Succubes fermente.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tes cheveux livreront leurs éclairs bleus et roux\nAu râle impérieux qui sourd de la tourmente,\nMais l’horreur d’être ne ploiera point nos genoux.\nDans nos yeux, le regard des Succubes fermente."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Les hommes ne verront nos ombres sur leurs seuils",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Qu’aux heures où, mêlant l’ardeur de nos deux haines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Nous serons les Banshees qui présagent les deuils,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et les Jettatori des naissances prochaines.",
